Tweens.lua

tweens:AnimCreate(table object, string value, number begin, number final, number time, string tweenname, string tweenmode)
First parameter: The table returned by the sprite
Second parameter: The value to be modified
Third parameter: The starting value
Fourth parameter: The final value
Fifth parameter: The duration of the animation
Sixth parameter: The name of the tween
Seventh parameter: The mode of the tween